      "blocks": {
        "q1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What does a Kérastase scalp serum actually do?",
            "content": "<p>It is a leave-on treatment (never rinsed out) that delivers concentrated actives straight to the scalp and root, applied to a towel-dried or dry scalp after washing. Depending on the variant, it reinforces the fiber against breakage (<a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-genesis-anti-hair-fall-fortifying-serum\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Genesis Anti Hair-Fall Fortifying Serum at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis</a>), builds the look of density (<a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-densifique-cure-femme\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Densifique Cure Femme Density Treatment (for Women) 6ml x 42 at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Densifique Cure</a>), clears dandruff overnight (<a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-symbiose-anti-dandruff-night-serum\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Symbiose Anti-Dandruff Night Serum at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Symbiose</a>), rebalances an oily or reactive scalp (<a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-specifique-potentialiste-serum\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Spécifique Potentialiste Balancing Scalp Serum 90ml at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Spécifique Potentialiste</a>), or strengthens a long grow-out (<a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-resistance-serum-extentioniste-50ml\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Resistance Extentioniste Sérum 50ml at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Extentioniste</a>). It is not a shampoo replacement — it is used after washing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which Kérastase serum is best for hair fall in the Philippines?",
            "content": "<p>For hair fall from breakage — the most common kind on chemically treated hair — the <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-genesis-anti-hair-fall-fortifying-serum\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Genesis Anti Hair-Fall Fortifying Serum at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis Anti-Hair Fall Fortifying Serum</a> is the first recommendation. For excessive shedding on thin, brittle strands, the <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-genesis-cure-anti-chute-anti-hairloss-treatment-6ml-x-42\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Genesis Cure Anti-Chute Anti-Hairloss Treatment 6ml x 42 at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis Cure Anti-Chute</a> six-week ampoule program goes deeper. Both are available at HairMNL.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which Kérastase serum is best for thinning or low-density hair?",
            "content": "<p>The Densifique Cure — a daily Stemoxydine scalp ampoule course that leaves thinning hair looking denser and thicker. It comes as the <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-densifique-cure-femme\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Densifique Cure Femme Density Treatment (for Women) 6ml x 42 at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Cure Femme</a> for women (42 ampoules of 6ml) and the <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-densifique-cure-homme-6ml-x-30\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Densifique Cure Homme Density Treatment (for Men) 6ml x 30 at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Cure Homme</a> for men (30 ampoules). It addresses the appearance of density, not new hair growth — and postpartum thinning in particular often resolves on its own as hormones settle.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which Kérastase serum treats dandruff?",
            "content": "<p>The <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/kerastase-symbiose-anti-dandruff-night-serum\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Symbiose Anti-Dandruff Night Serum at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Symbiose Anti-Dandruff Night Serum</a> — a leave-on serum that targets all types of dandruff and works overnight to help eliminate it at the source. For the full ritual, pair it with the Symbiose purifying anti-dandruff shampoo from the <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/collections/kerastase-symbiose\" title=\"Shop Kérastase Symbiose at HairMNL\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Kérastase Symbiose collection</a>. If your flaking is powdery and tight rather than oily, that is a dry scalp, not dandruff — Spécifique Potentialiste is the better match.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q5": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long does it take to see results?",
            "content": "<p>For the Genesis serum, continuous daily use is the key — most people notice reduced breakage around four to six weeks in. The ampoule programs are built as full courses: six weeks for the Genesis Cure, and the full box for the Densifique Cure (42 ampoules Femme, 30 Homme). Comfort-focused serums like Potentialiste can ease oiliness or irritation within days, and the Symbiose Night Serum works nightly toward lasting dandruff control. Consistency matters more than intensity.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is a Kérastase scalp serum worth it?",
            "content": "<p>A professional-grade scalp serum is a daily ritual, and a single bottle lasts months at a few drops per use — which makes the everyday investment modest for a salon-level formula. For better value, HairMNL often bundles serums with shampoos in travel and gift sets; check the Best Sellers collection for current sets.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
